entries.npc_1_1: Ello! Yousa got time to hep de Otoh Gunga Zoological Facility? My bein' Facility director. Wesa got a maxibig problem wit outlaunder tourists comen to Naboo and bringin' dey pet animals. De animals had gettin' loose, ruinin' de ecology. Deysa one beast, a blistmok, comen outen Talus. My needin' it killed. Okeyday?
entries.npc_2_1: Dissen what mesa want hearin'. Yousa go to work.
entries.npc_4_1: Itsa ittybitty reptavian ting wit maxibig blisters all over. Yousa not be touchin' dosa blisters, or yousa gettin' mooie-mooie bombad poison. Yousa takin' disa job?
entries.npc_backtowork_1: Yousa be gettin' to work soon, mesa hopin'.
entries.npc_reward_1: Mesa so smilen to hearin' yousa news. Mooie-mooie!
entries.npc_work_1: Yousa not findin' dat blistmok yet? Is a maxibig problem.
entries.npc_noloc_1: Wooah! Mesa datapad just now losin' de coordinates! Wesa gotten no more blistmok to be findin' right now. Yousa comin' back later.
entries.npc_failure_1: Oh, berry bombad. Tanks anyway. Wesa gonna find dat blistmok, yousa knowin' it.
entries.player_reset_1: I don't want this mission right now.
entries.player_sorry_1: I'll keep working on the mission.
entries.npc_1_2: Ello! Our scientists had figurin' out whatsa goin' on wit desa reports. Some virus is drivin' de animals cawazy. Yousa gotta kill desan latest intruders, duey bocatts outen Tatooine, so wesa can autopsy deysa brains!
entries.npc_2_2: Dissa just what my wantin' to hear. Yousa go puttin' down deysa bocatts.
entries.npc_4_2: A bocatt, hesa outlaunder reptavian-felinoid hybrid outa Tatooine. Bigga sharp teeth. Dey huntin' in pairs, usually, trackin' dere prey wit smellin'. Bombad nasty. So, yousa willin' to hep de Zoological Facility by killin' dese bocatts?

entries.npc_4_4: Des Corellian slice hound is messa dangerous predator. Desa attack anything... even Gungans... and desa mooie-mooie intelligent. Desa got mooie sharp teeth and spikes. Yousa be careful!
